{"word":"G1706 - ἐμπίπτω - empíptō - em-pip'-to - Fall among","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">empíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em-pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fall among</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அகப்படு, விழு"},{"paragraph":"to fall into"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>fall on</i>, that is, (literally) <i>be entrapped by</i>, or (figuratively) <i>be overwhelmed with:</i> - fall among (into).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}